OL,3,CVeteran rowing across Atlantic to
OL,4,CBarbados for charity
OL,6,FThey set off in December and have
OL,7,Ffaced storms, bad weather and big
OL,8,Fwaves as they make their way across
OL,9,Fthe Atlantic.
OL,11,FIn their latest video update posted on
OL,12,FWednesday 15 January, Chris said:
OL,13,F"We've been through the mill a bit but
OL,14,Fwe're not complaining because we're in
OL,15,Fparadise.
OL,17,F"We just want to put this message out
OL,18,Fthere for anyone who's struggling with
OL,19,Ftheir mental or physical health that
OL,20,Fthere's always light at the end of the
OL,21,Ftunnel.
