OL,3,CVeteran rowing across Atlantic to
OL,4,CBarbados for charity
OL,6,FHe served in Northern Ireland and
OL,7,FNorway, and was also a parachute-
OL,8,Ftrained operative on board an aircraft
OL,9,Fcarrier.
OL,11,FUpon leaving the military, Chris faced
OL,12,FPTSD and became homeless in the back
OL,13,Fstreets of Hong Kong.
OL,15,FHis first mate Louie, from Bolton, has
OL,16,Fserved on special operations with the
OL,17,FIrish Guards.
OL,19,FHe suffered a severe brain injury in
OL,20,F2021, but recently went on a skiing
OL,21,Fexpedition to the Arctic Polar Circle.
