OL,6,FThey are rowing the Atlantic to raise
OL,7,Fmoney for the charities Scotty's
OL,8,FLittle Soldiers, which supports
OL,9,Fbereaved service children, and
OL,10,FAlabare, which rehouses homeless
OL,11,Fveterans.
OL,13,FThe fundraiser has raised more than
OL,14,F#74,000 so far.
